is hand in the vessel\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13129,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/25\/not-rushing-through-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":34538,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Taking care not to rush through ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: We returned with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, from Mecca to Medina, until we found water by the road. Some people hurried to perform ablution for afternoon prayer, by the time we reached them their heels were dry and had not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26126,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/26\/masjid-women-leave-before-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":34538,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: The Prophet lets women leave before himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would end prayer with salutations of peace and remain in his place for a while. The Prophet would end prayer and the women would depart to enter their homes before he would depart. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 812 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41203,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/salah-make-up-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34538,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Performing make-up prayers after \u2018Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: By the One who took the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, he never left praying two missed cycles after the afternoon prayer until he met Allah Almighty, even when prayer became difficult for him. He used to perform many of his prayers while sitting down. The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":896,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/01\/prophet-does-chores\/","url_meta":{"origin":34538,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Chores: The Prophet does chores for his family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 1, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Aswad reported: I asked Aisha,\u00a0\u201cWhat did the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, do in his house?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cThe Prophet would do chores for his family and\u00a0he would go out\u00a0when it was time for prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 676 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0648\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25433,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/20\/salat-gentle-correction\/","url_meta":{"origin":34538,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet corrects his companion gently","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 20, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: He reached the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was bowing in prayer, so he bowed before joining the rows of prayer. It was mentioned to the Prophet and he said, \u201cMay Allah increase your eagerness, but do not do so again.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34538","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=34538"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34538\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=34538"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"cat